{
  "title": "Flaky Jamaican Rigatoni Pasta",
  "description": "A slow-cooked, paleo-friendly Jamaican dish featuring flaky rigatoni, infused with floral and monsoon-inspired flavors. This recipe combines the richness of coconut milk with the warmth of Caribbean spices.",
  "cuisine": "Jamaican",
  "diet": [
